{"article_id":"TrWXIO2JMZJQuoJT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"South Carolina Gov . Nikki Haley :","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"\" It Is Time","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"To Move The Flag. \"","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"On June 22 , NBC News reported","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that Governor Nikki Haley called on the state legislature to remove the Confederate battle flag from the state Capitol","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"following a mass shooting at a historically black church","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that killed 9 people :","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"South Carolina Gov . Nikki Haley called for the removal of the Confederate flag from the grounds of the state Capitol Monday ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"less than a week after a 21-year-old white man gunned down nine people at a historic African American church .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Support","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"for the flag to come down","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"from leaders around the state and around the country has been steadily growing in the wake of the devastating attack .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" Today , we are here in a moment of unity in our state ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"without ill will ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"to say","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"it is time","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"to move the flag from the Capitol grounds , \"","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Haley said during a news conference","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"attended by Republican senators Lindsey Graham and Tim Scott , along with other state leaders .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"[ NBC News , 6/22/15 ]","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Walmart , Amazon , Sears , And EBay Will No Longer Sell Confederate Flag Merchandise .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"According to CNN ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"the retailers Walmart , Amazon , Sears , and eBay announced","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"they will ban the sale of Confederate flag merchandise :","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"Walmart , Amazon , eBay and Sears all announced bans on the sale of Confederate flag merchandise , amid an intensifying national debate over the use of the controversial flag .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"The announcements are the latest indication","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that the flag , a symbol of the slave-holding South , has become toxic","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"in the aftermath of a shooting last week at a historic African-American church in Charleston , South Carolina .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Gov . Nikki Haley announced in a Monday afternoon news conference","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"that she supports removing the Confederate flag from the state capitol grounds .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"[ CNN , 6/23/15 ]","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Fox 's Guilfoyle :","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"\" Is The American Flag Next ? \"","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"During the June 23 edition of Fox News ' The Five , co-host Kimberly Guilfoyle responded to calls","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"for the Confederate battle flag to be removed from South Carolina 's Capitol grounds","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"by asking","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"whether the American flag would be next :","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"JUAN WILLIAMS :","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"I would just say , quickly , look at the fact","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that it was put up 100 years after the Civil War .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"So it 's not even people","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"who are grieving the deaths of the soldiers ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"it 's 100 years after","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"where people","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"who are seeking to defy Brown v. Board of Education ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"taking part in the massive resistance movement against integration , social integration , and political equality for blacks .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"GUILFOYLE :","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Is the American flag next ?","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"WILLIAMS :","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Oh , my God .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"I love the American flag !","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"It symbolizes the country","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"I love .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Why would I --","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"GUILFOYLE :","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"People can also try to suggest","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"that this was --","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"symbolizes wars , oppression .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"I was having a thoughtful conversation the other night with Laura Ingraham","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"and she was saying to me ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"you know ,","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"at one point is somebody going to say","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"they 're offended by this flag .","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"We see people disrespect the American flag .","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"[ Fox News , The Five , 6/23/15 ]","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Rush Limbaugh :","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"Removing Confederate Flag Is About \" Destroying The South. \"","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"On the June 23 edition of his radio program , Rush Limbaugh claimed","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that liberals ' true mission","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"in removing the Confederate flag in South Carolina","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"is \" destroying the South as a political force. \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Limbaugh then predicted ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"\" the next flag","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"that will come under assault ...","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"is the American flag \" :","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"LIMBAUGH :","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"It 's not going to stop with the Confederate flag ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"because it 's not about the Confederate flag .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"It is about destroying the South as a political force .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"It 's about isolating , targeting , and identifying the South as Dylann Roof . [ ... ]","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"The speed and rapidity","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"with which the left is conducting this assault on all of these American traditions and institutions --","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"if you do n't think","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"the American flag is in their crosshairs down the road ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"you had better stop","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"and reconsider .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"The American flag is what ?","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"It 's the symbol of America .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"The left , what ?","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Does n't like this country very much","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"and never has .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"[ Premiere Radio Networks , The Rush Limbaugh Show , 6/23/15 ]","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"Weekly Standard 's Bill Kristol :","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Liberals Are \" Expunging History In A Frenzy Of Self-Righteousness. \"","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"In a series of tweets on June 23 , The Weekly Standard editor Bill Kristol accused liberals of \" expunging every trace of respect , recognition or acknowledgment of Americans","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"who fought for the Confederacy . \"","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"Bill O'Reilly :","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"\" Historical Context \" Of Confederate Flag 'Represents Bravery . '","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Fox host Bill O'Reilly asserted","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"that the Confederate flag \" represents bravery \" on the June 22 edition of his program","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"telling Fox 's Juan Williams","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that \" it represents , to some , bravery in the Civil War","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"because the Confederates fought hard \"","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"( emphasis added ) :","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"O'RILLY :","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"You say","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"the Confederate flag is a symbol of hate","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"and you believe that .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"JUAN WILLIAMS :","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"That 's the way","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"I feel","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"when I see it .","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"O'REILLY :","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"Okay , okay .","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"And absolutely 100 percent legitimate .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"For some other people","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"who see it in a historical context --","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"WILLIAMS :","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"What 's the historical context ?","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"O'REILLY :","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"It represents bravery .","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"WILLIAMS :","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"Oh get out of town .","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"O'REILLY :","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"In war .","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"WILLIAMS :","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"They put it up in anger","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"when they were trying to mass resist the Civil Rights Movement in the 60 's .","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"O'REILLY :","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"You know","depth":16},{"id":130,"text":"as well","depth":17},{"id":131,"text":"as I do","depth":17},{"id":132,"text":"that it represents , to some , bravery in the Civil War","depth":16},{"id":133,"text":"because the Confederates fought hard . [ ... ]","depth":16},{"id":134,"text":"But that 's what it represents .","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"You 're right historically ,","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"but in their minds , that 's what it represents .","depth":15},{"id":137,"text":"And in your mind it represents hate .","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"So , and everybody should know","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"what the two sides are believing .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"[ Fox News , The O'Reilly Factor , 6/22/15 ]","depth":5},{"id":141,"text":"Fox 's Starnes :","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"\" The Cultural Cleansing Of The Southern States Begins. \"","depth":6},{"id":143,"text":"In a June 23 post on Fox Nation , Fox News Radio host Todd Starnes framed the South Carolina flag removal as \" a full-fledged cultural cleansing of the Southern states \" :","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":287,"left":146,"right":286,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":0,"right":145,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":207,"right":285,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":207,"left":173,"right":206,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":173,"left":162,"right":172,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":162,"left":151,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":149,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":3,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":4,"right":147,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":153,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":159,"right":19,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":157,"right":158,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":154,"right":156,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":14,"right":155,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":155,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":169,"right":171,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"